Company Description: Wendy's Is A Chain Of More Than 6,500 Hamburger Restaurants IN North America And Other International Markets. Founded IN 1969, The Chain S Restaurants Serve A Variety Of Hamburgers Made With Grilled Beef And Vegetable Toppings. Its Restaurants Also Serve Garden Salads, Grilled Chicken Sandwiches And Baked Potatoes. The Chain S Restaurants  Side Dishes Include French Fries, Chocolate Chip Cookies, Chicken Nuggets And Yogurt. Its Restaurants Also Offer Wendy S Kids  Meal. Wendy's Operates Bakeries That Supply Sandwich Buns. The Chain Additionally Participates IN Various Community Activities, Such As Animal Welfare Programs, Educational Plans And Foster Care Adoption Schemes. Wendy's Is Owned And Operated By Wendy S International.

Wendy's International Is A Chain Of Restaurants That Operates And Franchises More Than 6,500 Wendy's Restaurants IN The United States And IN 21 Other Countries As Well As Territories. Its Menu Includes Garden Sensations Salads, Combo Choices, Super Value Menu, Frosty Shakes And Frosty Float, Boneless Chicken Wings, Chicken Go Wraps And Signature Hamburger Offerings. The Company Is A Member Of Wendy's/Arby's Group Inc., The Third Largest Quick Service Restaurant Company IN The United States That Comprises The Wendy's And Arby's Brands.

Established IN 1969, Wendy's Is One Of The Quick-Service Food Chain Restaurants IN The United States. Based IN Brooklyn, N.Y., It Operates More Than 6,500 Wendy's Restaurants Throughout The United States And IN 21 Other Countries. A Member Of Arby's Group Inc., The Restaurant Offers A Menu, Which Includes Burgers, Hamburgers, Salads, Beverages And Combos. Specialty Menu Includes Old Fashioned Combos/Hamburgers, Home Style Chicken Go Wrap, Spicy Chicken Sandwich And Nuggets, Sweet And Spicy Asian Boneless Wings And Crispy Chicken Deluxe, To Name A Few. It Also Offers Special Items For Kids, Such As Mandarin Oranges, Nesquik Low Fat Chocolate Milk And Sandwiches.

Established IN 1969, Wendy's International Inc. Is A Chain Of Fast Food Restaurants. Based IN Copiague, N.Y., Wendy's Offers A Wide Range Of Meals, Including Combos, Hamburgers, Desserts And Hot/Cold Beverages. Some Of Its Flagship Products Include Old Fashioned Combos, Garden Sensations Salads, Wendy's Kids' Meal, Frosty And More. The Company Engages IN Numerous Community And Environment Initiatives, Such As Wendy's Animal Welfare Program, Wendy's Wonderful Kids And Others. Wendy's Is A Part Of The Wendy's/Arby's Group Inc., Which Is The Nation's Third Largest Quick Service Restaurant Company. It Is Ranked Top IN Various Categories IN Zagat's 2010 Fast Food Survey.
